14. Networking Strategy & Planning

15. Types of Architecture
15.1 Based on Communication: Client-Server, Peer-to-Peer, Hybrid Architecture
15.2 Based on Layering / Design: Monolithic, Tiered / n-tier (2,3, Multi), SOA (Service Oriented Architecture), Microservice, Event-Driven
15.3 Based on Networking Deployment: Centralized, Distributed, Cloud, Edge / Fog Computing
15.4 Specialized Architectures: Mesh, Star / Bus / Ring, Zero-Trust

