Layers 
Applications Layer - HTTP, HTTPS, FTP, SMTP, POP3, IMAP, DNS, DHCP, SNMP, Telnet, SSH, NTP
Presentation Layer - SSL/TLS, JPEG, GIF, MPEG, ASCII, EBCDIC, PNG, XML, JSON
Session Layer - NetBIOS, PPTP, RPC, SOCKS, SIP (VoIP sessions)
Transport Layer - TCP, UDP, SCTP
Network Layer - IP (IPv4/IPv6), ICMP, IGMP, IPsec, OSPF, RIP, BGP, ARP (often between L2/L3)
Data Link Layer - Ethernet (IEEE 802.3), PPP, HDLC, Frame Relay, ATM, VLAN (802.1Q), MPLS
Physical Layer - Ethernet cables, Wi-Fi (802.11), Bluetooth, DSL, RS-232, SONET, USB
